  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] You may return up to 4 Digimon cards
    with [Mamemon] in their names from your hand and/or trash to the top of your
    deck in any order. If you return 3 or more cards with this effect, \uFF1CDe-Digivolve
    1\uFF1E 1 of your opponent's Digimon. (Trash 1 card from the top of one of your
    opponent's Digimon. If it has no digivolution cards, or becomes a level 3 Digimon,
    you can't trash any more cards.)"
